  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>A comprehensive Player Controller that houses almost all game configuration</li><li>An Anomaly Actor and example anomalies</li><li>Camera Navigation</li><li>A minimal HUD</li><li>Choice to report with clicking, submitting a form, or both</li><li>An editor utility action to quickly replace static mesh actors with anomalies</li><li>A simple but effective difficulty mechanic</li><li>A debug widget to better visualize timings and difficulty</li><li>Documentation</li></ul><p>Number of Blueprints: 13 (&#43;5 examples)</p><p>Input: Keyboard and Mouse</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms:</p><p>Windows: Yes</p><p>Mac: No</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dO5NAmvjv8njIM37e-1AY2suQd-ZGYkm/view?usp&#61;drive_link\" rel=\"nofollow\">Google Drive</a></p><p>Important/Additional Notes:</p>",
